{
  "stem": "13258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And amazingly so, my-- her father was a, for that time, very progressive man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He insisted that his daughter have an education, which was rare at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of those, especially among Jewish people, also, thought that the-- the woman belongs in the house and in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Education wasn't important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father-- my grandfather said, if ever anything happens to a husband, if she gets one, but she was too young.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said if she ever gets one, she will have to be able to support herself if something happens to her husband.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, very much so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She helped, first of all, to support the family when my father lost his job with the German-- with the German language newspaper.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the war, when my father passed away during the war-- I think we'll get to that a little bit later-- but after the war, when she came out of-- first, when the war began, in the ghetto, she had to support herself.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then then when she came out of the camp, she had to support herself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she came to the United States, she had to support herself, even so after she got married a second time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her husband in the beginning, her second husband, in the beginning, didn't earn a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And besides, she still wanted to be independent because he had his own child from his first marriage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother had two children from her first marriage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she wanted to see if she can provide later on for the kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at one point, she worked for a brief time in a book and paper-- a stationary store to get a little bit more acquainted with the book trade.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
